title: Ep. 89 - Joey Chestnut Unfiltered
description:
The greatest Competitive Eating Champion to ever walk the earth popped in the studio to have an incredibly hilarious conversation with the boys. We had an absolute blast recording it and you'll have an absolute blast listening to it. We guarantee you've never heard American Legend Joey Chestnut let loose like this anywhere else.
